### Get Kitchen Schedule (Internal)
# Solver now filters and processes only Delivery Orders (CONFIRMED/PREPARING status)
# This trigger updates 'chefId' and 'expectedReadyAt' in the Order root.
POST http://localhost:5001/api/v1/internal/kitchen/schedule
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

{
  "tardiness_weight": 1000
}

### Get Delivery Schedule (VRP Solver) - POST
# Triggers a full solve (Kitchen + VRP) and returns the delivery schedule.
# This updates 'shipperId' and 'deliverySequence' inside the DeliveryOrder record.
POST http://localhost:5001/api/v1/internal/kitchen/delivery-schedule
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

{}

### Get Delivery Schedule (VRP Solver) - GET
# Returns the current delivery schedule from the database for the assigned shipper.
# Data is fetched from DeliveryOrder joined with Order and Store.
GET http://localhost:5001/api/v1/internal/kitchen/delivery-schedule
Authorization: Bearer {{shipperToken}}

